question: What are all the possible breed type and size type combinations?
verified_output: SELECT T3.charge_type ,  T2.breed_name ,  T1.size_description FROM Breeds AS T2 JOIN Treatments AS T4 ON T2.breed_code = T4.treatment_type_code    JOIN Charges AS T3 ON T3.charge_id = T4.dog_id    JOIN Sizes AS T1 ON T1.size_code = T4.treatment_type_code

question: List the first name of all the professionals along with the description of the treatment they have done.
verified_output: SELECT T5.first_name FROM Sizes AS T4 JOIN Dogs AS T2 ON T4.size_code = T2.size_code    JOIN Owners AS T5 ON T5.owner_id = T2.owner_id    JOIN Professionals AS T1 ON T1.professional_id = T2.owner_id    JOIN Treatments AS T3 ON T3.treatment_id = T2.dog_id
